targets.rawSql:
SELECT
	start_date AS "Start",
	end_date AS "End",
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM start_date))*1000 AS start_date_ts,
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM end_date))*1000 AS end_date_ts,
	'üöó Drive' AS "Action",
	drives.duration_min AS "Duration",
	CASE WHEN start_geofence_id IS NULL THEN CONCAT('new?lat=', TP1.latitude, '&lng=', TP1.longitude)
		WHEN start_geofence_id IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(start_geofence_id, '/edit')
	END AS start_path,
	CASE WHEN end_geofence_id IS NULL THEN CONCAT('new?lat=', TP2.latitude, '&lng=', TP2.longitude)
		WHEN start_geofence_id IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(end_geofence_id, '/edit')
	END AS end_path,
	COALESCE(start_geofence.name, CONCAT_WS(', ', COALESCE(start_address.name, nullif(CONCAT_WS(' ', start_address.road, start_address.house_number), '')), start_address.city)) AS "Start Address",
	COALESCE(end_geofence.name, CONCAT_WS(', ', COALESCE(end_address.name, nullif(CONCAT_WS(' ', end_address.road, end_address.house_number), '')), end_address.city)) AS "End Address",
	convert_km(TP1.odometer::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS odometer_$length_unit,
	convert_km(distance::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS distance_$length_unit,
	convert_km((end_[[preferred_range]]_range_km - start_[[preferred_range]]_range_km)::INTEGER, '$length_unit') * cars.efficiency AS "kWh",
	convert_km((end_[[preferred_range]]_range_km - start_[[preferred_range]]_range_km)::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS range_diff_$length_unit,
	TP2.battery_level AS "SoC",
	TP2.battery_level-TP1.battery_level AS "SoC Diff",
	outside_temp_avg AS outside_temp_avg_$temp_unit
FROM drives
	LEFT OUTER JOIN positions AS TP1 on drives.start_position_id = TP1.id
	LEFT OUTER JOIN positions AS TP2 on drives.end_position_id = TP2.id
	LEFT JOIN addresses start_address ON start_address_id = start_address.id
	LEFT JOIN addresses end_address ON  end_address_id = end_address.id
	LEFT JOIN geofences start_geofence ON start_geofence_id = start_geofence.id
	LEFT JOIN geofences end_geofence ON end_geofence_id = end_geofence.id
	JOIN cars ON cars.id = drives.car_id
WHERE 
	$__timeFilter(drives.start_date)
	AND	drives.car_id = $car_id
	AND	'üöó Drive' in ($action_filter)
	AND	('Start Address' like '%$text_filter%' or 'End Address' like '%$text_filter%')

UNION
SELECT
	start_date AS "Start",
	end_date AS "End",
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM start_date))*1000 AS start_date_ts,
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM end_date))*1000 AS end_date_ts,
	'üîã charges' AS "Action",
	charging_processes.duration_min AS "Duration",
	CASE WHEN geofence_id IS NULL THEN CONCAT('new?lat=', address.latitude, '&lng=', address.longitude)
		WHEN geofence_id IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(geofence_id, '/edit')
	END AS start_path,
	null AS end_path,
	COALESCE(geofence.name, CONCAT_WS(', ', COALESCE(address.name, nullif(CONCAT_WS(' ', address.road, address.house_number), '')), address.city)) AS "Start Address",
	'' AS "End Address",
	convert_km(position.odometer::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS odometer_$length_unit,
	null AS distance_$length_unit,
	convert_km((end_[[preferred_range]]_range_km - start_[[preferred_range]]_range_km)::INTEGER, '$length_unit') * cars.efficiency AS "kWh",
	convert_km((end_[[preferred_range]]_range_km - start_[[preferred_range]]_range_km)::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS range_diff_$length_unit, 
	end_battery_level AS "SoC",
	end_battery_level - start_battery_level AS "SoC Diff",
	outside_temp_avg AS outside_temp_avg_$temp_unit
FROM charging_processes
	INNER JOIN positions AS position ON position_id = position.id
	LEFT JOIN addresses address ON address_id = address.id
	LEFT JOIN geofences geofence ON geofence_id = geofence.id
	LEFT JOIN cars on cars.id = charging_processes.car_id
WHERE
	$__timeFilter(charging_processes.start_date)
	AND charging_processes.car_id = $car_id
	AND 'üîã charges' in ($action_filter)
	AND	('Start Address' like '%$text_filter%' or 'End Address' like '%$text_filter%')


UNION
SELECT
	T1.end_date AS "Start",
	T2.start_date AS "End",
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM T1.end_date)) * 1000 AS start_date_ts,
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM T2.start_date))*1000 AS end_date_ts,
	'üÖøÔ∏è Parking' AS "Action",
	EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM T2.start_date - T1.end_date)/60 AS "Duration",
	CASE WHEN T1.end_geofence_id IS NULL THEN CONCAT('new?lat=', TP1.latitude, '&lng=', TP1.longitude)
		WHEN T1.end_geofence_id IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(T1.end_geofence_id, '/edit')
	END AS start_path,
	null AS end_path,
	COALESCE(start_geofence.name, CONCAT_WS(', ', COALESCE(start_address.name, nullif(CONCAT_WS(' ', start_address.road, start_address.house_number), '')), start_address.city)) AS "Start Address",
	'' AS "End Address",
	convert_km(TP1.odometer::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS odometer_$length_unit,
	null AS distance_$length_unit,
	convert_km(((TP2.ideal_battery_range_km + (TP2.odometer - TP1.odometer)) - TP1.ideal_battery_range_km)::INTEGER, '$length_unit') * efficiency AS "kWh",
	convert_km(((TP2.ideal_battery_range_km + (TP2.odometer - TP1.odometer)) - TP1.ideal_battery_range_km)::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS range_diff_$length_unit,
	TP2.battery_level AS "SoC",
	TP2.battery_level-TP1.battery_level AS "SoC Diff",
	T1.outside_temp_avg AS outside_temp_avg_$temp_unit
FROM
	drives AS T1
	LEFT OUTER JOIN drives AS T2 on T1.id + 1 = T2.id
	LEFT OUTER JOIN positions AS TP1 on T1.end_position_id = TP1.id
	LEFT OUTER JOIN positions AS TP2 on T2.start_position_id = TP2.id
	LEFT JOIN addresses start_address ON T1.end_address_id = start_address.id
	LEFT JOIN addresses end_address ON T2.start_address_id = end_address.id
	LEFT JOIN geofences start_geofence ON T1.end_geofence_id = start_geofence.id
	LEFT JOIN geofences end_geofence ON T2.start_geofence_id = end_geofence.id
	JOIN cars ON cars.id = T2.car_id
WHERE
	$__timeFilter(T1.end_date)
	AND T1.car_id=$car_id
	AND TP1.ideal_battery_range_km <> TP2.ideal_battery_range_km
	AND TP2.car_id=$car_id
	AND TP1.car_id=$car_id
	AND 'üÖøÔ∏è Parking' in ($action_filter)
	AND ('Start Address' like '%$text_filter%' or 'End Address' like '%$text_filter%')

UNION
SELECT
	T1.end_date AS "Start",
	T2.start_date AS "End",
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM T2.start_date)) * 1000 - 1 AS start_date_ts,
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM T2.start_date))*1000 - 1 AS end_date_ts,
	'‚ùì Missing' AS "Action",
	EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM T2.start_date - T1.end_date)/60 AS "Duration",
	CASE WHEN T1.end_geofence_id IS NULL THEN CONCAT('new?lat=', TP1.latitude, '&lng=', TP1.longitude)
		WHEN T1.end_geofence_id IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(T1.end_geofence_id, '/edit')
	END AS start_path,
	CASE WHEN T2.start_geofence_id IS NULL THEN CONCAT('new?lat=', TP2.latitude, '&lng=', TP2.longitude)
		WHEN T2.start_geofence_id IS NOT NULL THEN CONCAT(T2.start_geofence_id, '/edit')
	END AS end_path,
	COALESCE(start_geofence.name, CONCAT_WS(', ', COALESCE(start_address.name, nullif(CONCAT_WS(' ', start_address.road, start_address.house_number), '')), start_address.city)) AS "Start Address",
	COALESCE(end_geofence.name, CONCAT_WS(', ', COALESCE(end_address.name, nullif(CONCAT_WS(' ', end_address.road, end_address.house_number), '')), end_address.city)) AS "End Address",
	convert_km(TP1.odometer::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS odometer_$length_unit,
	convert_km((TP2.odometer - TP1.odometer)::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS distance_$length_unit,
	convert_km(((TP2.ideal_battery_range_km + (TP2.odometer - TP1.odometer)) - TP1.ideal_battery_range_km)::INTEGER, '$length_unit')::INTEGER * efficiency AS "kWh",
	convert_km(((TP2.ideal_battery_range_km + (TP2.odometer - TP1.odometer)) - TP1.ideal_battery_range_km)::INTEGER, '$length_unit') AS range_diff_$length_unit,
	TP2.battery_level AS "SoC",
	TP2.battery_level-TP1.battery_level AS "SoC Diff",
	T1.outside_temp_avg AS outside_temp_avg_$temp_unit
FROM
	drives AS T1
	LEFT OUTER JOIN drives AS T2 on T1.id + 1 = T2.id
	LEFT OUTER JOIN positions AS TP1 on T1.end_position_id = TP1.id
	LEFT OUTER JOIN positions AS TP2 on T2.start_position_id = TP2.id
	LEFT JOIN addresses start_address ON T1.end_address_id = start_address.id
	LEFT JOIN addresses end_address ON T2.start_address_id = end_address.id
	LEFT JOIN geofences start_geofence ON T1.end_geofence_id = start_geofence.id
	LEFT JOIN geofences end_geofence ON T2.start_geofence_id = end_geofence.id
	JOIN cars ON cars.id = T2.car_id
WHERE
	$__timeFilter(T1.end_date)
	AND T1.car_id=$car_id 
	AND T2.car_id=$car_id 
	AND TP2.car_id=$car_id 
	AND TP1.car_id=$car_id 
	AND TP2.odometer - TP1.odometer > 0.5
	AND T1.end_address_id <> T2.start_address_id AND T1.end_geofence_id <> T2.start_geofence_id
	AND '‚ùì Missing' in ($action_filter)
	AND ('Start Address' like '%$text_filter%' or 'End Address' like '%$text_filter%')

UNION
SELECT
	start_date AS "Start",
	start_date AS "End",
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM start_date))*1000 AS start_date_ts, 
	ROUND(EXTRACT(EPOCH FROM start_date))*1000 AS end_date_ts, 
	'üíæ Update' AS "Action",
	null AS distance_$length_unit,
	null AS start_path,
	null AS end_path,
	version AS "Start Address",
	'' AS "End Address",
	null AS odometer_$length_unit,
	null AS "Distance", 
	null AS "kWh",
	null AS range_diff_$length_unit,
	null AS "SoC",
	null AS "SoC Diff",
	null AS outside_temp_avg_$temp_unit
FROM updates
WHERE 
	$__timeFilter(start_date)
	AND car_id = $car_id 
	AND 'üíæ Update' in ($action_filter)

ORDER BY "Start" DESC
